(4,'Index','Chateau Towns Markham by Regency','Welcome to Chateau Markham Towns, an exclusive new community set amidst the energy of a dynamic, flourishing city.','/img/home/banner.jpg','index','no',0,'en','/','/','index.html','../html/en/pages/index.html','<article id=\"home\" class=\"home\" aria-label=\"Main Content Body\" role=\"main\">\r\n\r\n	<section class=\"masthead js-animate\" config-animation-better=\"100\">\r\n			\r\n			<div class=\"masthead\">\r\n						<img  src=\"/img/home/banner.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\r\n						<div class=\"logos\">\r\n								<a href=\"/\"><img  src=\"/img/logo2.svg\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\r\n								<a href=\"/\"><img  src=\"/img/logo-chateau2.svg\" alt=\"Image\"></a>\r\n								<p>Coming Soon</p>\r\n								<a href=\"#registration\" class=\"scrolling btn\">REGISTER NOW</a>\r\n						</div>\r\n			</div>	\r\n	</section>		\r\n	\r\n	<section class=\"full js-animate slide-in-bottom\"  config-animation-better=\"100\" >		\r\n			\r\n			<div class=\"content\">\r\n					<h1>Towns by Regency</h1>\r\n					<p>Welcome to Chateau Markham Towns, an exclusive new community set amidst the energy of a dynamic, flourishing city. Blending classic elegance with modern luxury, these meticulously crafted homes offer inspiring spaces to savour every moment. Experience the ease and access of top-ranked schools, tranquil green space, and today’s most desirable urban amenities – all in Markham, where the quality of life is unsurpassed and valued. </p>\r\n			</div>\r\n	</section>		\r\n\r\n	\r\n	<section class=\"full js-animate slide-in-bottom\"  config-animation-better=\"100\" >		\r\n			<div class=\"content\">\r\n					<div class=\"grid-1 animation-slide-up animation-waterfall\">\r\n							<img  src=\"/img/home/1.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\r\n							<img  src=\"/img/home/2.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\r\n							<img  src=\"/img/home/3.jpg\" alt=\"Image\">\r\n					</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n\r\n	</section>		\r\n\r\n	<section class=\"full js-animate slide-in-bottom\"  config-animation-bett