ennedy Station on TTC Line 1 and Major Mackenzie Dr., connecting with all the major east-west YRT lines.</p></div>\r\n																	</div>\r\n															</div>\r\n															<div>\r\n																	<div class=\"transit-point\">\r\n																			<div><p>Viva Bus Rapid Transit</p><span class=\"c-blue\">Bus 129a</span></div>\r\n																			<div><p>Bus 129A also connects with the Viva Bus Rapid Transit (BRT) line on Highway 7, which offers high-frequency, limited-stop service.</p></div>\r\n																	</div>\r\n														</div>											\r\n												</div>\r\n									</div>\r\n							</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n	</section>		\r\n\r\n	<section class=\"full js-animate slide-in-bottom\"  config-animation-better=\"100\" >		\r\n			<div class=\"area-map\">\r\n					<img  src=\"/img/area/map.png\" alt=\"Image\">\r\n					<div class=\"legend\">\r\n									<div>\r\n											<div class=\"js-accordion\">\r\n													<h4>SHOPPING</h4>\r\n													<div>\r\n															<ol>\r\n																<li>CF Markville Mall </li>\r\n																<li>FoodyMart supermarket</li>\r\n																<li>T&T Supermarket Unionville Store</li>\r\n																<li>Loblaws Bullock Drive</li>\r\n																<li>LCBO</li>\r\n																<li>Whole Foods Market </li>\r\n																<li>Costco Wholesale</li>\r\n															</ol>\r\n													</div>\r\n											</div>\r\n											<div class=\"js-accordion\">\r\n													<h4>RESTAURANTS & CAFES</h4>\r\n													<div>\r\n															<ol>\r\n																<li>Ruth’s Chris Steak House</li>\r\n																<li>Watercolour Mediterranean Restaurant Unionville</li>\r\n																<li>Il Postino</li>\r\n																<li>JOEY Markville</li>\r\n																<li>Kiu Japanese Restaurant</li>\r\n																<li>Terre Rouge Event Venue</li>\r\n																<li>Starving Artist Waffles & Espresso</li>\r\n																<li>Behind The Alley</li>\r\n																<li>Old